{
  "name": "Monitor stock levels with HTTP / REST API and Telegram without manual work",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "days",
              "daysInterval": 1,
              "triggerAtHour": 8
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "c98bdb0b-958e-49e8-8554-3b0563beb5d6",
      "name": "Schedule Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [
        320,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "51b831d7-0254-4615-9380-716f72998b7f",
              "name": "receivedAt",
              "value": "={{ $now.toISO() }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "69849f5d-0a66-44b1-8179-5f5a7210bab0",
              "name": "isValid",
              "value": "={{ $json ? true : false }}",
              "type": "boolean"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "79dcba66-383c-4525-8099-493393d63a25",
      "name": "Validate Input",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [
        560,
        300
      ],
      "notes": "Validate & normalize the input before downstream steps (§9.1)."
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://api.example.com/v1/data",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "62da9679-51cf-46e3-8061-468203e0713b",
      "name": "Fetch Data",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        800,
        300
      ],
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 3,
      "waitBetweenTries": 2000
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "typeValidation": "loose",
            "version": 2
          },
          "combinator": "and",
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "788285d1-e176-452c-89d7-19a4b500f03a",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.status }}",
              "rightValue": "high",
              "operator": {
                "type": "string",
                "operation": "equals"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "4a95c9ce-5f72-451c-b591-b877d76f82b1",
      "name": "Route on Condition",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [
        1040,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "message",
        "operation": "sendMessage",
        "chatId": "={{ $json.chatId }}",
        "text": "={{ $json.summary || 'Update' }}",
        "additionalFields": {}
      },
      "id": "d7c5828a-394a-43f7-9d25-bb978a1ede8e",
      "name": "Send Telegram Message",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.telegram",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [
        1280,
        300
      ],
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 3,
      "waitBetweenTries": 2000
    },
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "id": "9c3e2d46-dd2d-4070-98a9-7045fd412bab",
      "name": "Skip (No Action)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.noOp",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1280,
        500
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Monitor stock levels with HTTP / REST API and Telegram without manual work\n\n**Pattern:** Threshold Monitoring\n**Trigger:** Scheduled\n**Integrations:** HTTP / REST API, Telegram\n\nImport, add your credentials, then adjust parameters. Original FlowDex template.",
        "height": 260,
